    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and an ionic current knock sensing system to deliver a linear 414 hp powerband peaking at 8,300 RPM. The chassis maintains its composure via Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque vectoring across the rear axle. This example features the 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission for lightning-fast shifts. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, the subframe remains intact and the rod bearings have been proactively addressed. A driver\u2019s spec machine ready for the apex.",
